## Why This Is Asked

Tests ability to design automated IR in Azure at scale, integrating Key Vault, Sentinel, Runbooks, and network isolation.

## Key Concepts

- Key Vault rotation and secret versioning
- Azure Sentinel detection rules and alerting
- Automation Runbooks or Logic Apps
- Private Endpoints and NSGs
- Azure AD session revocation and PIM

## Code Example

```javascript
// Pseudo-IR runbook snippet (Azure SDK)
async function rotateSecret(vaultName, secretName){
  const newValue = generateSecret();
  await secretClient.setSecret(vaultName, secretName, newValue);
  await aadClient.revokeUserSessions('compromised-id');
}
```

## Follow-up Questions

- How would you test the rollback path under partial failure?
- How do you ensure no downtime during rotation?

## Why This Is Asked
